#-------------------
# Tetromino I
#-------------------

OrientationCount:       2
Rotateable:             yes, 2 times
Reflectable:            no
RaflectableOptionally:  no
TransformationType:     TwoOrientations

Orientations:

NORMAL_0        NORMAL_90

4.....          4.....
3D....          3.....
2C....          2.....
1B....          1.....
0A....          0ABCD.
 01234           01234

A = (0, 0)      A = (0, 0)
B = (0, 1)      B = (1, 0)
C = (0, 2)      C = (2, 0)
D = (0, 3)      D = (3, 0)

